Design a premium enterprise SaaS web application called Livlong AI Insurance Intelligence Platform.

The application is an AI-powered Insurance Broker CRM + Business Intelligence + Analytics + Automation Platform inspired by Microsoft Power BI Copilot, Salesforce Einstein, Microsoft Fabric, Tableau Pulse, Notion AI, and Stripe Dashboard.

The UI should look like a 2026 modern enterprise product with glassmorphism, soft shadows, rounded cards (18px), subtle gradients, smooth animations, premium typography, excellent spacing, and a clean professional design.

Primary colors:

Blue (#2563EB)
Indigo
White
Light Gray
Emerald for success
Orange for warnings
Red for critical alerts

Use Inter or SF Pro font.

Create realistic mock data throughout the application.

