Every page should contain an AI Insights Panel on the right with natural-language business analysis and actionable recommendations. Use realistic insurance industry mock data across all dashboards, ensuring the prototype feels like a production-ready AI platform that could compete with Power BI Copilot, Salesforce Einstein, and Tableau Pulse.